# Test Plan - OpenCart E-Commerce Application

## 1. Introduction
This document describes the test plan for OpenCart demo e-commerce web application.

## 2. Scope
### In Scope:
- User Registration
- Login
- Product Search
- Add to Cart
- Checkout Process

### Out of Scope:
- Payment Gateway real transactions
- Admin Panel

## 3. Test Strategy
Manual functional testing will be performed on all major modules.

## 4. Test Environment
- Browser: Chrome, Edge
- OS: Windows 10
- Tools: Jira, Excel, GitHub

## 5. Entry Criteria
- Application should be accessible
- Test cases should be prepared

## 6. Exit Criteria
- All critical test cases executed
- Major bugs reported

## 7. Roles and Responsibilities
QA Engineer: Khushbu Rajak

## 8. Risks
- Demo site instability
- Limited real payment testing
